               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250407-156-cd840" type="crimeDate">12th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250407-156-off839 t18250407-156-cd840"></join>, a crown piece and a sixpence, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18250407-156-victim860" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Hurley
                     <interp inst="t18250407-156-victim860" type="surname" value="Hurley"></interp>
